Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.69,0:00:02.61,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,This here is Blueberry Academy!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.61,0:00:05.69,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Incredible! \N So there really {\i1}is{\i0} a school in the ocean!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.99,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Whoa! There’s loadsa Pokémon \N I’ve never seen before!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.41,0:00:12.70,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,This place is mega-perfect \N for training, ain’t it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.12,0:00:16.58,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Look! \N The Pokémon are Terastallized, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.62,0:00:20.25,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,There’s Terastal here, there, \N and everywhere! It’s sparkling!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.25,0:00:23.54,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And so, to be continued \N next time on Pocket Monsters!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.63,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tera{\fnHummingMod}☆{\fn}Sparkling! Blueberry Academy
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.63,0:00:28.09,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Now, let’s get down to training!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.93,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
